Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:23.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:34.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう言って彼女はうつむいてたんだ　夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:41.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷たく貼り付いて　凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:48.86,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降り続く現実に　傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:55.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きてゆくことが　戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.33,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな理由だけで　閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:02.22,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart　My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:09.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:16.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:23.16,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah  ah　鳥のように　飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:34.64,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませたとき　感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:42.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:23.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在傷害別人之前　不必強顏歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:34.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說著她低下頭　在黑夜裡哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:41.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷黏合在一起　渾身僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:48.86,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下個不停　卻沒有傘來遮擋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:55.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己囚禁在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.33,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有戰鬥才能求生的因果之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:02.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心　我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:09.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淚水的彼岸所見到的　是五彩光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:16.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的窗口　映照出那時蔚藍的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:23.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　雖說不能像鳥兒一樣自由翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:34.64,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害別人之後的那份心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不忘卻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:42.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕地閉上眼　哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:55.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}#22  為了未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·修亨伯格製造出Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  製造出GN Drive的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武力介入只是佈局
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導人類走向革新
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我…要進行變革
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.16,0:00:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變革？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你所追求的極致嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being  再次出現…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次請務必給我與之戰鬥的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所追求的是作為戰鬥者所能到達的極致
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那少年曾說我扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我就是個只能與他戰鬥的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才期望著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取得這極致的勝利！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.99,0:01:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只期望勝利嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其它的嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用問？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接著未來的明天！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格殺勿論！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空手奪白刃？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰…戰鬥吧  少年…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親手把我劈開  並抓住這勝利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不給我最後一擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著抓住明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了活著而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈  路易斯·哈萊維的機體呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有反應  好像已經撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是突然想這麼說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為純種而覺醒了嗎？  刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是掌握人類命運的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說知道吠陀所在的地方了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是來自王留美的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到吠陀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加密信息解析完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點是CZ9842R  是月球的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜  用超望遠攝影機觀測一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格朗日2…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連殖民地開發都沒有開始進行的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為隱藏地點相當不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將目標地點圖像表示在顯示器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個位置的星圖和畫面重疊在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星的位置有所偏移
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是光學迷彩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把偏離的距離算出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離是  直…直徑15千米
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有15千米？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有那麼大的東西藏在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在月球的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  實驗室的運輸艦發來加密通信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新裝備來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨立治安維持部隊A-LAWS\N將用全部戰力進行對Celestial Being的殲滅作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將作為反政府勢力最後堡壘的他們打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏得統一世界的真正和平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待著諸位的奮戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21艘巡洋艦和108台MS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼多的戰力的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準將  那些有特殊許可的傢伙離開艦隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他們  就算他們在戰場上亂來也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李本茲發來的返回命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他終於下決心了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  跟計劃一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為即將到來的東西迫在眉睫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯·哈萊維…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人的仇？  我也有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為不幸的只有自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活該…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把能成為戰力的東西都帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各機的強化部件及托勒密的補給物資…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連O Gundam都帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為裝上了粒子儲藏設備  能進行一定時間的戰鬥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！  趕快搬進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美指定的地點有艦隊在集結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯了  吠陀就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者的總部也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破A-LAWS艦隊並奪回吠陀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是場前所未有的激戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去吧  為了進行我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛斯勞德君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定了  不會再迷茫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我也參加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇摩·佩麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有這麼做的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  即使目的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都有各自前往那裡的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  這些想法都連接著未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了未來而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了把人類從改革者的支配下解放出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了世界上不再出現像我或者蘇摩·佩麗絲這樣的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒聯邦政府是我的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙擊改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要改變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不改變的話  就不會有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成補給之後  托勒密就立刻出發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  現在的托勒密還少一個舵手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在這裡嗎
