Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是尋求死亡之道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了活著而戰
