Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑他們的戰力… 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準將  我方的運輸艦有異樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運輸艦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子光束發射過來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勸告A-LAWS艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們奮起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淪為聯邦惡政之傀儡的A-LAWS已非軍隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界前進的方向只應遵從於市民的合意而決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現將汝等之暴行定罪  以向市民問求是非
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個狐狸精…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊潰他們！ 那是反政府勢力！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方部隊接近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS隊  開始攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死之身的克拉薩烏  參上！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一艘運輸艦都搞不定  你們在做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們躲在僚艦後面  無法攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能動的己方留著有什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不分敵友全都給我打下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是裡面還有我方的士兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了  給我射擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準將！ 敵艦突破Anti-Field了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G…Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO-Raiser  驅逐目標！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給…給我想想辦法！
