Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將他們引導至此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該也是你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.87,0:23:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是位於你們上位的物種
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可說是創造主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢  你沉迷於野心的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就通過腦量子波知道得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.43,0:23:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾  李傑尼·雷傑塔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.32,0:23:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李本茲·阿爾馬克！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…  是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.23,0:23:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導人類的將是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李傑尼·雷傑塔！
